u2013 Peak tourist season (Nov\u2011Feb) is busy; book hotels & activities **at least 2\u202fweeks** in advance.  \\n\\n---\\n\\n### Ready to Book?  \\n\\n- **Flights**: Look for budget carriers (IndiGo, SpiceJet) \u2013 round\u2011trip from major Indian metros \u2248\u202f\u20b96,000\u2011\u20b99,000.  \\n- **Hotel**: Use the links below (they have \u201cinstant\u2011confirm\u201d rates).  \\n- **Activities**: Pre\u2011book the spice\u2011plantation tour and any water\u2011sports via **Klook** or **Viator** for guaranteed slots.  \\n\\nEnjoy your Goa adventure \u2013 sun, sea, spice, and a dash of nightlife, all within your \u20b950k budget! \ud83c\udf1e\ud83c\udfd6\ufe0f\ud83c\udf64\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Planner\"}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_1d335231-7f6e-44a1-bb6c-636acea1df9a/1d335231-7f6e-44a1-bb6c-636acea1df9a", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
