etail'` error and let your TravelBot fetch Google Maps data (or raise a meaningful custom exception) without crashing. Happy coding! \ud83d\ude80\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Planner\"}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_1d335231-7f6e-44a1-bb6c-636acea1df9a/1d335231-7f6e-44a1-bb6c-636acea1df9a", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
